<p begin='00:04:50.457' end='00:04:55.963' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>I DIDN&apos;T KNOW THIS.</span></p>
<p begin='00:04:55.996' end='00:04:57.097' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>&gt;&gt; IT&apos;S FICTION.</span></p>
<p begin='00:04:57.097' end='00:05:00.334' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>&gt;&gt; Stephen: YOU CAN GO INTO<br/>YOUR OWN MIND AND SURPRISE</span></p>
