<p begin='00:05:05.138' end='00:05:07.541' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>&gt;&gt; Stephen: THIS BEING AMERICA,<br/>WERE YOU PACKING HEAT?</span></p>
<p begin='00:05:07.574' end='00:05:08.375' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'> &gt;&gt; NO.</span></p>
<p begin='00:05:08.408' end='00:05:09.476' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>BUT ALL MY CRIMINAL FRIENDS TOLD<br/>ME TO.</span></p>
<p begin='00:05:09.510' end='00:05:11.612' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>ALL THE PEOPLE I KNOW IN JAIL<br/>SAID, TAKE A GUN.</span></p>
