<p begin='00:05:35.169' end='00:05:40.474' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>&gt;&gt; Stephen: THAT IS WONDERFUL<br/>ADVICE THAT FOR LEGAL REASONS I</span></p>
